    "{'preparing cold meal'} B.5 ADL-LLM w/o EnvThis approach differs from ADL-LLM only in the system prompt, where the description of the monitored rooms and household items is omitted.",
    "B.5.1 System prompt.Act as a human activity recognition system that infers the activities performed by a subject in their home.",
    "I will provide you with a description of what happened during a specific time window, and your goal is to provide the most likely activity.",
